data.description: FABULOUS LOCATION!  Situated a block from West Street and minutes to downtown Annapolis.  This home is ready for your creative ideas.   When you first approach this beauty you will see the grand porch, which can't be beat!  This is a wonderful part of the home.  Imagine your afternoons, sitting on the porch, visiting with friends and neighbors, enjoying a refreshment!  A front porch and one this size is a definite positive feature.  When you enter the home you will notice the spacious entryway with the wooden staircase leading upstairs.  The main level is a traditional style.  On the right side is the proper living room with wood burning fireplace.  From the living room you can go into the separate and formal dining room.  There is plenty of space in the dining room for china cabinets and a large table.  Plenty of entertaining space.  From the dining room there is the kitchen with large pantry attached.  In the kitchen is the door to the exterior back of the home.  On the upper level you will find four roomy bedrooms and a full bath.  On the lower level/basement level there is the washer dryer and space to finish off!  Parking is on street but you could possibly take out the fence near the rear of the yard on Morris and put in a parking pad/driveway.  Otherwise the living and entertaining space out back is awesome.  Plenty of room to barbecue and entertain!   This classic home is being sold in AS IS condition.   Thank you for showing.
